data.description: This beautiful home sits in a park like setting with mature trees and great landscaping surrounding the home.  The 4 bedroom, 2 bathroom home sits on over 3 acres.  There is a nice deck on the front of the home and a very private covered deck on the back of the home.  One of the greatest features of the home is the oversized 2 car garage with a large workshop.  The garage and workshop are both insulated and heated.  There is a breezeway in between the home and the garage/shop.  The property has a barn as well as a chicken coop and stalls for livestock.  The property is fenced and cross-fenced.  The irrigation water keeps this property lush and green.  There are multiple apple trees, as well as a pear and peach tree.  This property is a must see.  CALL for a showing today.
